{"id": 2849, "genre": 1001, "title": "日常中你都有哪些“间歇式热爱生活”的表现？", "description": "我对生活的积极性都是平时潜伏、偶尔发作的那种。（题图来自：iStock ©️ cosmaa）", "record_count": 3917, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190317203455S4sbIgTfLkYOEhvc.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-03-21T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 334848, "content": "去公园拍花", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1484590}, {"id": 334849, "content": "放假前，把假期计划的十分自律。放假后，宅在家吃＋睡。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1596218}, {"id": 334850, "content": "突然有一种极度想学习的欲望，过会儿就忘了", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1506544}, {"id": 334851, "content": "把游戏都删了打算认真学习认真生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1615516}, {"id": 336131, "content": "太阳☀️出来了就忍不住把自己能晒的东西都抱出来晒。晒过太阳后散发出来的味道最好闻了🤗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1621760}, {"id": 334852, "content": "突然间按规律作息，过后又是颠倒黑白。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1615519}, {"id": 336132, "content": "把屋子收拾的干干净净的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1620576}, {"id": 335877, "content": "拼命的打扫卫生，洗衣服", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1620535}, {"id": 334854, "content": "有那么几天起劲儿把工作都做得差不多了 剩下的几天每天发呆", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1043664}, {"id": 334856, "content": "阶段性做好减肥计划，永远在美食与懒惰之间屈服", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1615535}, {"id": 334857, "content": "开始大洗衣服", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1512774}, {"id": 334858, "content": "竟然睡好觉了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1163079}, {"id": 335627, "content": "运动", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1619143}, {"id": 334862, "content": "看了好奇心日报后开始思考人生", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1298793}, {"id": 335118, "content": "买菜、烧饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1616496}, {"id": 334607, "content": "我正好相反，偶尔会需要放肆一下，大部分时间比较自律", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1614866}, {"id": 335887, "content": "每日都有那么几个小时极度热爱学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1603624}, {"id": 334608, "content": "放假之后，无聊之前的时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1135562}, {"id": 335636, "content": "我每天都热爱生活，不间歇", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1619204}, {"id": 334613, "content": "间歇，性热爱，持续，性冷淡", "image": null, "praise_count": 334, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1227284}, {"id": 333590, "content": "平时不整理，心血来潮会把屋子收拾得像样板间", "image": null, "praise_count": 1129, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 334614, "content": "收拾房间，弄乱，再收拾的过程", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 128838}, {"id": 333591, "content": "一连好几天自己认真做饭，剩下的日子靠外卖维生", "image": null, "praise_count": 173, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 334615, "content": "突然五分钟对工作很有热情", "image": null, "praise_count": 221, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1611049}, {"id": 333592, "content": "不怎么照顾自己，但总会记得给养的植物浇水", "image": null, "praise_count": 64, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 333593, "content": "天气好了就积极洗衣打扫，一下雨就不想动", "image": null, "praise_count": 214, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 335385, "content": "周末晚上认真做下一周的计划。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1493295}, {"id": 334874, "content": "偶尔反思，想要振作起来，就在闲鱼上买超多工作相关的课程，买了就算看了......", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1381892}, {"id": 336154, "content": "突然这段时间热爱某种兴趣，比如玩乐高，会买很多，疯狂拼到怀疑人生，就冷淡了，要好久才能再玩", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1498015}, {"id": 334620, "content": "对某种活动心血来潮，配齐装备，整装上阵。但没过多久热情全无，装备也就闲置吃灰。", "image": null, "praise_count": 71, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1612214}, {"id": 334877, "content": "突然给自己做了一顿饭，被难吃到了，又默默点起了外卖。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1601901}, {"id": 334623, "content": "工作期间 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1572527}, {"id": 335135, "content": "对每件身边的事物都不由自主露出姨母笑？？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1616618}, {"id": 334624, "content": "隔一段时间，会对衣柜摆放的衣服产生兴趣，全部拿出来重新整理摆放整齐", "image": null, "praise_count": 45, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 438248}, {"id": 334625, "content": "淘宝收藏一堆家居装饰，没买过几个", "image": null, "praise_count": 79, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1561503}, {"id": 334882, "content": "间歇性收拾屋子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1615601}, {"id": 334627, "content": "定个六点的闹钟", "image": null, "praise_count": 168, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1352500}, {"id": 334883, "content": "收拾书桌泡好花茶调好灯光准备做文案，然后点开网易云听歌听了一下午🤔", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531372}, {"id": 334885, "content": "一个人去公园", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1495626}, {"id": 335141, "content": "每个月都给自己买束花插在花瓶里，但很少修剪或换水，任花凋零。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1177168}, {"id": 334886, "content": "打开健身APP做运动", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1367354}, {"id": 334632, "content": "总是给自己每个小玩具", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1613880}, {"id": 334889, "content": "起得来就吃早饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1615663}, {"id": 334890, "content": "准备学习新的东西 从入门到放弃", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1614921}, {"id": 334635, "content": "脑子里画张饼，做梦就实现了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 78222}, {"id": 334636, "content": "早上，一定要精神饱满努力工作；下午，人间不值得", "image": null, "praise_count": 144, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1373857}, {"id": 334892, "content": "平时颓着，心血来潮想干点啥就去干，心里想着这就是热爱生活。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1615682}, {"id": 335404, "content": "大概就是 走着走着跑步的兴致高涨，开跑的时候就累了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1615113}, {"id": 334893, "content": "日常表现不就说明问题了吗？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1262396}, {"id": 334638, "content": "整理书桌，衣柜，开始看诗歌，画画，唱歌🎤做个面膜，跑步锻炼，化个全妆，穿裙子，好像自己过得精致又美好。。怎么都有人要一样。。😂", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1584526}]}